{
  "stem": "23278.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had my papers, and my uncle was the mayor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was-- still, he was not pursued yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was still OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To go to see  my grandma.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was vacation, it was summer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Rita came-- it was in September.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "School starts in October there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's in the-- what did I do with my little-- my little pictures?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, don't-- you can't get up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it's '83.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, '42.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1942.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let me see, yes, '42.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they both went-- succeeded through other means, not mine, to go to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Switzerland, they were not well treated by, by the family of her mother in Basel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not welcome.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were not happy there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rita's grandmother.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She had been the wife of the grand rabbi.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she had died, and the grand rabbi had remarried.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So Rita was with her grandmother-- not with her grandfather, but with her step grandmother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was very unhappy there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bad times.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, she survived the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when she was at my grandmother-- the grandfather-- the father was caught.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he became the-- he was-- he had the Iron Cross from the First World War.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had been a captain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But as I told you before, he had enlisted in the French army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he kept both on himself, which was silly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So for the Germans, he was a traitor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Thalmann is not a Jewish name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then they discovered he was Jewish, you know, the usual means.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he became the orderly of an SS who kicked him to death.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He died in Auschwitz, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very nice story, eh?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
